{"case_id": "challenge-coding-003", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "topological-sort"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 1024, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "413c5b602b0fd1ae1e9c3a49b09ecf03c61769fce4b34dbd96b5d8c6a2c68f90", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:38:19.522207+00:00", "latency_ms": 7870, "output": "```python\nfrom collections import defaultdict\n\ndef solve(deps: dict[str, list[str]]) -> list[list[str]]:\n    nodes = set(deps.keys())\n    for pres in deps.values():\n        nodes.update(pres)\n\n    indeg = {u: 0 for u in nodes}\n    adj = defaultdict(list)\n    for u, pres in deps.items():\n        for v in pres:\n            adj[v].append(u)\n            indeg[u] += 1\n\n    layer = sorted([u for u, d in indeg.items() if d == 0])\n    result = []\n    seen = set()\n\n    while layer:\n        result.append(layer)\n        seen.update(layer)\n        nxt = []\n        for u in layer:\n            for w in adj[u]:\n                indeg[w] -= 1\n                if indeg[w] == 0:\n                    nxt.append(w)\n        layer = sorted(nxt)\n\n    if len(seen) != len(nodes):\n        return []\n    return result\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 102, "completion_tokens": 497, "total_tokens": 599, "cost": 0.0020849, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0020849, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 9.69e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.001988}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 287, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781584701-xZ4zSfZ6pMR3MHMFdU3t", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-004", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "lru"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 1024, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "840e7b4d0c404f3d7b34ebc9931e87612608d6339755d5f1066fda55bd957375", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:38:27.433987+00:00", "latency_ms": 6894, "output": "```python\nfrom collections import OrderedDict\n\ndef solve(capacity: int, ops: list[str]) -> list[int]:\n    cache = OrderedDict()\n    out = []\n    for op in ops:\n        parts = op.split()\n        if parts[0] == \"get\":\n            key = int(parts[1])\n            if capacity == 0 or key not in cache:\n                out.append(-1)\n            else:\n                cache.move_to_end(key)\n                out.append(cache[key])\n        elif parts[0] == \"put\":\n            key = int(parts[1])\n            value = int(parts[2])\n            if capacity == 0:\n                continue\n            if key in cache:\n                cache[key] = value\n                cache.move_to_end(key)\n            else:\n                if len(cache) == capacity:\n                    cache.popitem(last=False)\n                cache[key] = value\n    return out\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 117, "completion_tokens": 489, "total_tokens": 606, "cost": 0.00206715, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00206715, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.00011115, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.001956}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 302, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781584709-ioBmuxcoWIFQTbd5AN94", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": false, "score": 0.0, "details": {"returncode": 1, "stdout": "", "stderr": "Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"/var/folders/x_/4cht1kfj1_j31gdv5w0