{"case_id": "challenge-coding-005", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "json", "copy"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 1024, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "8dc22406b418d74ea74b50692fe086d4f80748258269dc93f82290e6c344b5a3", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:38:34.369858+00:00", "latency_ms": 15988, "output": " ```python\nimport copy\nfrom typing import Any, Dict\n\ndef solve(base: Dict[str, Any], patch: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    result = copy.deepcopy(base)\n    for key, value in patch.items():\n        if value is None:\n            result.pop(key, None)\n        elif isinstance(value, dict) and isinstance(result.get(key), dict):\n            result[key] = solve(result[key], value)\n        else:\n            result[key] = copy.deepcopy(value)\n    return result\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 93, "completion_tokens": 338, "total_tokens": 431, "cost": 0.00144035, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00144035, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 8.835e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.001352}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 261, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781584716-iqap3SeO7Y3aVmrpGkuq", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
{"case_id": "challenge-coding-006", "suite": "coding", "case_version": "0.2.0", "tags": ["python", "regex", "duration"], "model": "moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code", "provider": null, "parameters": {"temperature": 0, "max_tokens": 1024, "seed": null}, "prompt_hash": "ce87366a2f6f080a35c0fdd0872b6a8304a8233e0c5c9361c19fec614c0d1fcb", "started_at": "2026-06-16T04:38:50.532737+00:00", "latency_ms": 35221, "output": "```python\nimport re\n\ndef solve(text: str) -> int:\n    units = {\"d\": 86400000, \"h\": 3600000, \"m\": 60000, \"s\": 1000, \"ms\": 1}\n    total = 0\n    for m in re.finditer(r\"(\\d+)\\s*(ms|[dhms])\", text):\n        total += int(m.group(1)) * units[m.group(2)]\n    return total\n```", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 93, "completion_tokens": 683, "total_tokens": 776, "cost": 0.00282035, "is_byok": false, "prompt_tokens_details": {"cached_tokens": 0, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.00282035, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 8.835e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.002732}, "completion_tokens_details": {"reasoning_tokens": 578, "image_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0}}, "response_id": "gen-1781584733-1MmrshMvowMuu3Ri2Eza", "finish_reason": "stop", "score": {"passed": true, "score": 1.0, "details": {"returncode": 0, "stdout": "", "stderr": ""}}, "error": null}
